[normal]the “hockey stick” was the star of Assessment Report 3 (AR3) in 2001 and was included in AR4 in 2007.  The hockey stick claimed that the global temperature declined since about 1000 to the end of the nineteenth century,
[normal] when it has been increasing due to CO2
